As tricks go, walking on water is right up there with turning water into wine.

However, some daredevil paragliders manage to make the seemingly impossible look easy - as they come in to land in France.

A video captures the two men drifting over Morzine, in the Rhone-Alpes, with one performing an 360-degree spin over a sheer rock face before skimming the water of a lake for a stylish landing.

